 picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1705195,"age":8,"year":"1382","julianDay":2225826,"title":"Wycliffe's Bible","description":"John Wycliffe, English theologian and professor at the University of Oxford, completed a translation of the Bible from the Latin Vulgate into Middle English. This translation is known as Wycliffe's Bible and was completed around 1382.","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wycliffe%27s_Bible","urlTitle":"Wikipedia - Wycliffe's Bible","jurisdictionLevel":1}],"lifeSummary":"When William Brace was born in 1374, in Warndon, Worcestershire, England, his father, William Brace, was 35 and his mother, Joan, was 24. He married Isabella in 1400, in Madresfield, Worcestershire, England. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. He died before 6 February 1450, in Worcestershire, England."},"et":{"1374–before 6 February 1450":"1374–enne 6. veebruari 1450","1374–1450":"1374–1450","1383–1439":"1383–1439","1404–1476":"1404–1476","1400–1476":"1400–1476","1340–1390":"1340–1390","1351–1390":"1351–1390","6 FEB 1450":"15. veebruar 1450","1374":"1374","1373":"1373","1351":"1351","1340":"1340","1450":"1450","1383":"1383","Abt 1400":"umbes 1400","1382":"1382","before 6 February 1450":"enne 6. veebruari 1450","1390":"1390","1404":"1404","1400":"1400","1476":"1476","1431":"1431","10 March 1439":"10. märts 1439","Abt 1390":"umbes 1390","1429":"1429","Aft 1390":"pärast 1390","1439":"1439","Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, England","Warnedon, Worcester, England":"Warndon, Worcestershire, England","Madresfield, Worcestershire, England, United Kingdom":"Madresfield, Worcestershire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Madresfield, Worcestershire, England":"Madresfield, Worcestershire, England","France":"Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1374–before 6 February 1450":"1374–ennen vuotta 6. helmikuuta 1450","1374–1450":"1374–1450","1383–1439":"1383–1439","1404–1476":"1404–1476","1400–1476":"1400–1476","1340–1390":"1340–1390","1351–1390":"1351–139